### Acceptance criteria — Phase 1

- Clicking "Today" in the FilterBar date presets shows only assets with `taken_at` (or
  `file_mtime` fallback) matching today's date; chiclet reads "📅 Mar 22, 2026".
- Clicking "This month" shows assets from March 1–22, 2026 (current date); chiclet reads
  "📅 Mar 2026".
- Custom range: entering from=2024-01-01 to=2024-12-31 and clicking Apply shows 2024 assets.
- Removing the date chiclet returns to un-date-filtered browse/search.
- In the Lightbox, the `taken_at` date is underlined on hover and shows a tooltip "Filter to
  this date". Clicking it: lightbox closes, grid shows that day's assets, path/tag/q preserved.
- When no `taken_at` is available, the date field shows `file_mtime` in the lightbox and
  clicking it still works.
- When `taken_at` is null AND `file_mtime` is null, no date field is shown in the lightbox
  (unchanged from current behavior).
- All existing Vitest tests pass. The `onDateClick` prop is optional so no call sites break.

