### Acceptance criteria — Phase 3

- Pressing `F` in the lightbox enters fullscreen; `F` again or `Esc` exits. The fullscreen
  button icon toggles between expand/contract arrows.
- In fullscreen mode the metadata panel is hidden; only the image and nav arrows are visible.
- On lightbox open, keyboard hints appear for 3 seconds then fade out. Pressing `?` toggles
  them permanently on/off.
- GPS coordinates are a tappable/clickable link; clicking opens Google Maps at the correct
  location in a new tab.
- Pressing `Space` starts slideshow; images advance every 3 seconds; a progress bar sweeps
  across the top. Pressing `Space` again stops it. Manual next/prev navigation also stops it.
